snippet.title: LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures New Trailer
snippet.description:
Brand new LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures Trailer for the Xbox 360, PS3 and Nintendo Wii. Looks good so enjoy the video.

Release Date: 
June 3, 2008 (North America) 
June 4, 2008 (Australia) 
June 6, 2008 (Europe)
